value.description:
In order to promote community construction and encourage more institutions and individuals to participate in the ecological construction of CoinEx Chain, the CoinEx Chain Foundation hereby launches a support program

1. Application Support Categories
Product R&D (such as APP, wallet, explorer, etc.)
Community (Group) Construction
Content Publicity

2. Application Standard
Any validators, institutions, and individuals who have contributed to the CoinEx Chain ecosystem can log in to the CoinEx Chain official forum https://forum.coinex.org/ in the CoinEx Chain Chinese or English section of Foundation to submit online application quarterly

3. Award Levels and Amounts
Product R&D/Community(Group) construction/Content publicity: Gold (1 winner) — 300,000 CET
Product R&D/Community(Group) construction/Content publicity: Silver (2 winners) — 200,000 CET
Product R&D/Community(Group) construction/Content publicity: Bronze (3 winners) — 100,000 CET

-------------------------

CoinEx Chain基金会扶持奖励计划

为促进社区建设，鼓励更多机构和个人参与到CoinEx Chain的生态建设中，CoinEx Chain基金会特此发起扶持奖励计划

一、申请扶持类别
产品开发类（如APP、钱包、浏览器等）
社区（群）建设类
内容宣传类

二、申请标准
任何对CoinEx Chain生态做出贡献的验证节点、机构及个人等均可每季度登录CoinEx Chain官网论坛 https://forum.coinex.org/ 的CoinEx Chain中文区或英文区的“基金会”分区进行在线申请参与扶持奖励申请

三、扶持等级及额度
产品开发/社区（群）建设/内容宣传类特等（1名）：30万CET
产品开发/社区（群）建设/内容宣传类一等（2名）：20万CET
产品开发/社区（群）建设/内容宣传类二等（3名）：10万CET
value.title: CoinEx Chain Foundation Support Program

value.description:
Proposal on shortening the voting period of the CoinEx Chain proposal
The voting period of 14 natural days is too long, which is not good to the development of CoinEx Chain. Therefore, the CETDAC propose to change the voting period from 14 natural days to 7 natural days.

关于调整CoinE Chain 提案投票周期缩短的提案
14个自然日的投票周期过于冗长，不利于CoinEx Chain发展。因此CETDAC节点提议，将投票周期从14个自然日到7个自然日。
value.title: Change CoinEx Chain Proposal Voting Period to 7 days

现有的CoinEx Chain DEX发币成本极高，严重影响发币体验以及整体发展。
因此，联合 喵星电台发起关于降低CoinEx Chain DEX发币成本的提案：发行2字母token成本从100k CET降低至10k CET，发行3 & 3+字母token的成本从10k CET 降低至 1k CET，请大家支持，谢谢！

The current CoinEx Chain DEX issuance cost is extremely high, which seriously affects the issuance experience and overall development.
Therefore, the and propose to reduce the cost of CoinEx Chain DEX coin issuance as below:
1. the cost of issuing a 2-letter token was reduced from 100k CET to 5k CET
2. the cost of issuing a 3 & 3+ letter token was 10k CET reduced to 500 CET.
please support , highly appreciate！
